title: 2019 Week 17 Recap
itunes:title: 2019 Week 17 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal recap every game of week 17 starting with the SNF showdown between the 49ers and Seahawks (3:20). The Saints destroy the Panthers (11:55) and the Packers get a first round bye (17:52) while the Patriots do not for the first time this decade. (22:54). Stick around for the ramifications of the Bengals Browns game at the end of the show. (1:29:15)
